					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-997140#post-2095817</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-997140/scp-2913#post-2095817</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sun, 24 Aug 2014 12:34:10 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Doctor Cimmerian</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1414765</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Not if the hand would be perfectly happy with it's owner under normal circumstances. It's not that kind of hand. ;)</p> <p>I tried to be subtle about it. I mean for example the hand refers to James' sister and dad as though they were it's own family. It grew up as the guy's hand, it doesn't know much else other than that. It's why even when it's free, it's content to just lay around and watch TV. Hell, it couldn't even conceive of the idea of true freedom(that of being detached), and only ended up completely free by accident.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
